query: How many transactions were made by customers who have a loan?
What is the total balance of accounts belonging to customers who also have a deposit?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    SUM(A.account_balance) AS total_balance
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" C
JOIN 
    banking_new."Accounts" A ON C.customer_id = A.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Deposits" D ON C.customer_id = D.customer_id AND D.deposit_type_id IN (SELECT deposit_type_id FROM banking_new."DepositTypes")
GROUP BY 
    C.customer_id;

query: What is the number of customers who have both a loan and a deposit?
What is the total loan balance for customers who own at least one card?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    C.customer_name,
    COALESCE(SUM(L.balance), 0) AS total_loan_balance
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" C
JOIN 
    banking_new."Cards" B ON C.customer_id = B.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Loans" L ON B.customer_id = L.customer_id
GROUP BY 
    C.customer_name;

query: What is the total deposit balance for customers who made at least one transaction?
How many transactions were made by customers who belong to branch 1?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM banking_new."Customers" c 
JOIN banking_new."Branches" b ON c.branch_id = b.branch_id 
JOIN banking_new."Accounts" a ON c.customer_id = a.customer_id 
JOIN banking_new."Transactions" t ON a.account_id = t.account_id 
WHERE b.branch_code = '1';

query: What is the total number of accounts for customers who belong to each branch?

SELECT

    COUNT(DISTINCT a.account_id) AS total_accounts
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" c
JOIN

JOIN 
    banking_new."Accounts" a ON c.customer_id = a.customer_id
GROUP BY 
    b.branch_code;

query: What is the total loan balance for customers from branch 3?
What is the number of blocked cards belonging to customers with loans?
What is the number of expired cards belonging to customers with deposits?
What is the number of accounts created before 2020 for customers with loans?
What is the number of deposits created after 2021 for customers with cards?
What is the number of loans created in the last year for customers with transactions?
What is the total transaction amount of customers with deposits?
What is the total transaction amount of customers with loans?
What is the average number of accounts per customer?
What is the average number of loans per customer?
What is the average number of deposits per customer?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    COALESCE(COUNT(DISTINCT banking_new."Deposits".deposit_identifier), 0) / COUNT(banking_new."Customers".customer_id)

query: What is the total balance of accounts for customers who have more than one card?
What is the number of customers with both blocked and expired cards?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.customer_id)
FROM banking_new."Customers" c
JOIN banking_new."Cards" card ON c.customer_id = card.customer_id
WHERE card.is_blocked = TRUE AND card.expiration_date < CURRENT_DATE;

query: What is the total deposit balance for customers who also made more than 5 transactions?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    COALESCE(SUM(d.balance), 0) AS total_deposit_balance
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" c
JOIN 
    banking_new."Deposits" d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Transactions" t ON d.deposit_id = t.account_id
WHERE 
    c.customer_id IN (
        SELECT 
            account_id
        FROM 
            banking_new."Transactions"
        GROUP BY 
            account_id
        HAVING 
            COUNT(*) > 5
    );

query: What is the total transaction amount for customers who own more than one account?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    C.customer_name,
    COALESCE(SUM(T.transaction_amount), 0) AS total_transaction_amount
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" C
JOIN 
    banking_new."Accounts" A ON C.customer_id = A.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Transactions" T ON A.account_id = T.account_id
GROUP BY 
    C.customer_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT A.account_id) > 1;

query: What is the number of accounts belonging to customers with blocked cards?
What is the total loan balance for customers with expired cards?
What is the total number of deposits for customers with more than one loan?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.customer_id) 
FROM banking_new."Customers" AS T1 
JOIN banking_new."Loans" AS T2 ON T1.customer_id = T2.customer_id 
WHERE T2.loan_type_id IN (SELECT loan_type_id FROM banking_new."LoanTypes" WHERE type LIKE '%more than one%') 
AND T1.customer_id NOT IN (
  SELECT T3.customer_id 
  FROM banking_new."Customers" AS T3 
  JOIN banking_new."Loans" AS T4 ON T3.customer_id = T4.customer_id 
  GROUP BY T3.customer_id 
  HAVING COUNT(T4.loan_type_id) > 1
);

query: Count the number of transactions in the last month per account.

FROM

query: How many transactions were made in accounts belonging to customers with loans?
What is the total account balance of customers who made transactions this year?
sql_command:
SELECT 
    COALESCE(SUM(A.account_balance), 0) AS total_account_balance
FROM 
    banking_new."Customers" C
JOIN 
    banking_new."Accounts" A ON C.customer_id = A.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Transactions" T ON A.account_id = T.account_id
WHERE 
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM T.transaction_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)
GROUP BY 
    C.customer_name;
